{"tid":1056504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府：建議醫療券使用視光服務上限每兩年兩千元","createTime":"2019-03-11T09:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T09:06:52.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06c5a4d8d25d151cdeaad330a36dea363c80d885","tid":1056504,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T09:06:42.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府建議為長者醫療券用於視光服務的金額上限，設定為每兩年2000元計劃今年第二季實施。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局向立法會提交文件，參考視力檢查的市場價格及其他福利計劃配置眼鏡的金額，曾考慮將上限設為每兩年1000元，諮詢病人組織及持份者意見後，理解1000元上限會令部分長者自付較高金額，亦留意到相關專業組織關注這上限屬相當低的水平，因此參考去年視光服務每宗醫療券申報金額中位數，調高上限至2000元。<br />\n<br />\n有關措施計劃在今年第二季實施。"},{"pid":"8336050d24bacdc3fa6bd9bcbee1ebc8f3785acb","tid":1056504,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T09:06:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=340445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D340445&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=597d154d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D340445&h=41431df4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=340445</a>"}]}